  "detailed_description": "<strong>MADE IN OHIO</strong> is an EPIC First Person game 👍<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279390/extras/840c1164e48ed11d98ce89ee961b181c.avif?t=1679442175\" width=587 height=147 /></span><br>Play versus the most powerful meme and <strong>HISTORICAL</strong> characters of all times  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279390/extras/02b718708a2cbf28fb682500389a0641.webp?t=1679442175\" width=32 height=32 /></span><br><br>You will be followed by faithful guide <strong><i>El GATO</i></strong> during you adventures in OHIO :) <br><strong>NEVER</strong> underestimate him!<br>He is small but quite powerful  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279390/extras/3e5c518ab315f1da821147c00a2dd962.webp?t=1679442175\" width=32 height=32 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Exciting Gameplay<br></li><li> Strategical Moves<br></li><li> Boss Fights<br></li><li> Sliding <u>SusMan</u><br></li><li> El GATO</li></ul><strong><u>Challenge Yourself! Can you survive in OHIO?</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279390/extras/841b5525e7f251266cf543af5ea34a19.poster.avif?t=1679442175\" width=420 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279390/extras/841b5525e7f251266cf543af5ea34a19.webm?t=1679442175\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279390/extras/841b5525e7f251266cf543af5ea34a19.mp4?t=1679442175\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
